ed houses and minimising wastage by using prefabricated or modular elements. During design and construction, incorporate approaches that will make it easier to adapt, reuse and eventually dismantle the building. By choosing durable, low maintenance materials, you can minimise the need for new materials and finishes over the building’s lifetime.\r\n\r\nThe next step is to select materials with low environmental impact. Put simply, a ‘sustainable’ material is one that does not impact negatively on non-renewable resources, the natural environment or human health. Most products have a net-negative impact on the environment; however, it’s important to minimise the negative impacts of any materials you choose. When looking at the environmental impact of a material or product, consider all stages of the life cycle that are the upstream stage, the in-use or operational stage, and the downstream stage.\r\n\r\nInformed decisions about materials and construction systems can significantly reduce the environmental impact of a home without adding to the cost.','Choose building materials wisely','','publish','open','open','','energy-saving','','','2015-08-25 03:11:15','2015-08-25 03:11:15','',0,'http://localhost:8888/?p=32',0,'post','',1),(33,1,'2015-08-22 09:36:04','2015-08-22 09:36:04','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, sumo conceptam definiebas sed id, ad vix legere detracto, ne vim ullum commune. Te his assum scriptorem. Dolorem instructior his id, at fugit ubique est, in justo oporteat conceptam sit. Ex velit eripuit senserit quo, id mel alii feugiat.\r\n\r\nCum an choro intellegebat. Natum populo signiferumque ut nec. Est veri malorum ullamcorper ad, ea eum copiosae percipit salutatus, id idque reprimique nam. Tempor ignota adipisci id pro, iusto civibus ea sea.\r\n\r\nAgam simul usu te. Possim mnesarchum vel in, te debet movet ignota vix. Ius ex legimus dolores disputando, quodsi adipiscing repudiandae est ad. Minim laudem animal usu eu, erant definitionem ea qui, possim voluptat