irs and/or carnivals which would take place in and around their community.\r\n\r\nWith regarding to the rating of the house, we can tie-up with an assessor who has received NatHERS* accreditation from a relevant organisation like Association of Building Sustainability Assessors (ABSA) and Building Designers Association of Victoria (BDAV) to provide a credible rating.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n*Note: - Nationwide House Energy Rating Scheme (NatHERS) is a framework which supports the efforts of Australian governments to reduce the energy and greenhouse gas impact of residential buildings.','Future','','publish','closed','closed','','future','','','2015-08-25 03:09:36','2015-08-25 03:09:36','',0,'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=52',0,'page','',0),(53,1,'2015-08-23 02:23:06','2015-08-23 02:23:06',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','53','','','2015-09-05 08:01:52','2015-09-05 08:01:52','',0,'http://localhost:8888/?p=53',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(54,1,'2015-08-23 02:23:06','2015-08-23 02:23:06','Lorem porttitor hac turpis rhoncus penatibus adipiscing, dignissim arcu urna odio tincidunt, urna tortor ut. Nunc ut, lacus! Tempor purus proin ac quis lectus placerat elit lacus sagittis, tincidunt porttitor vel phasellus elit, diam elementum? A scelerisque eu scelerisque tortor, enim sit, turpis et. Tincidunt pulvinar magna cras, pid ut purus aliquet tempor sit, dictumst habitasse, velit vut tristique porta sit nascetur enim amet tortor massa? Elementum in duis arcu etiam sit. In sed ut, magnis velit porttitor elementum cursus porta aliquam sed sociis, platea cum, augue. Lundium amet nisi aliquam, vel! Dictumst adipiscing? Elementum pulvinar! Duis magna vel rhoncus natoque nunc nunc ultricies! Scelerisque? Vel dignissim! Porttitor, cum enim placerat elementum, massa dis? Aliquam odio urna. Vel natoque enim turpis, dictumst pulvinar tincidunt et mattis, augue scelerisque dolor ut quis lacus enim eu velit, parturient in amet integer sociis, et elit augue tempor. Habitasse mattis rh